snippet: Egypt's public prosecutor charged 200 suspected Islamist militants on Saturday with "founding, leading and joining a terrorist organisation" and launching bomb and rocket attacks across the country....

headline.print_headline: Egypt Charges 200 Islamist Militants With Bombings, Other Violence
headline.main: Egypt Charges 200 Islamist Militants With Bombings, Other Violence

lead_paragraph: Egypt's public prosecutor charged 200 suspected Islamist militants on Saturday with "founding, leading and joining a terrorist organisation" and launching bomb and rocket attacks across the country.
